{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775838430862,"sessionID":"ses_287ca279cffe3fzcCE8xiTi9ES","part":{"id":"prt_d7835f105001H4atAtzlRJFoc3","messageID":"msg_d7835e450001dyPRtvBFR81pY9","sessionID":"ses_287ca279cffe3fzcCE8xiTi9ES","type":"tool","tool":"task","callID":"call_4c012149c2594e338324e1a4","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"description":"Explore agentcube project structure","prompt":"Explore the agentcube project at /home/dsj/benchmark to understand:\n1. The overall project structure (top-level directories)\n2. What `pkg/picod` contains (if it exists) or what `picod` relates to\n3. Any existing proposals or design docs (look for proposal.md, design.md, etc.)\n4. The CRD types for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter (look in pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/)\n5. Any existing deployment or command execution related code\n6. What \"PicoD\" means in this context - search for picod references\n\nReturn a comprehensive summary of findings including file paths and key code structures.","subagent_type":"explore"},"output":"task_id: ses_287ca0112ffebH4ZRvUNS1F2UU (for resuming to continue this task if needed)\n\n<task_result>\nHere is a comprehensive summary of the AgentCube project based on my thorough exploration.\n\n---\n\n## 1. Overall Project Structure (Top-Level Directories)\n\nThe benchmark root at `/home/dsj/benchmark` is an **SDD-TEE evaluation framework** (Spec-Driven Development Token Efficiency Evaluation) that evaluates AI coding assistants against the real open-source project **agentcube** (`github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube`). The actual agentcube code lives in the workspace subdirectory.\n\n**Benchmark root** (`/home/dsj/benchmark`):\n| Directory | Purpose |\n|-----------|---------|\n| `configs/` | Evaluation configuration (tools, models, AR lists) |\n| `docs/` | Documentation |\n| `results/` | Evaluation outputs (JSON data, HTML reports, logs) |\n| `scripts/` | Core logic scripts (schema validation, report generation, data collection) |\n| `specs/` | Reverse-engineered OpenSpec specifications for agentcube |\n| `workspaces/` | Real-time evaluation code (the actual agentcube implementations) |\n| `proposal.md` | AR-001: CRD AgentRuntime type definition proposal |\n| `PLAN.md` | Implementation plan for AR-023 through AR-033 |\n| `README.md` | SDD-TEE evaluation framework documentation |\n| `Makefile` | Build automation |\n\n**AgentCube workspace** (`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z`):\n| Directory | Purpose |\n|-----------|---------|\n| `pkg/` | Core Go packages (router, store, apis, workloadmanager, common/types) |\n| `client-go/` | Generated Kubernetes typed client, informers, listers |\n| `changes/` | Change request directories (AR-001 through AR-015+), each with design.md, proposal.md, tasks.md |\n| `cmd/` | (Not present in this workspace snapshot; referenced in design docs) |\n| `specs/` subdirs | `sandbox-orchestration/`, `session-routing/`, `session-store/`, `code-execution/`, `deployment/`, `idle-cleanup/`, `ci-cd/`, `cli-toolkit/`, `integrations/`, `python-sdk/`, `testing/` |\n| `go.mod` | Go module: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube` (Go 1.25.0) |\n\n---\n\n## 2. What `pkg/picod` Contains (or Relates To)\n\n**`pkg/picod` does NOT exist as a directory in the current workspace.** However, it is extensively referenced throughout the codebase and specs. Here is what PicoD is:\n\n**PicoD** is a lightweight HTTP daemon that runs inside sandbox pods to handle command execution and file management. It is the **code execution engine** inside each sandbox container.\n\n### Key PicoD Specifications (from `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/code-execution/spec.md`):\n\n- **Purpose**: HTTP daemon that runs commands inside a configurable workspace jail, manages workspace files, and exposes a health endpoint with JWT (RSA)-protected APIs.\n- **API Endpoints**:\n  - `POST /api/execute` -- Execute commands with timeout, working directory, and environment augmentation\n  - `POST /api/files` -- File upload (multipart or Base64 JSON)\n  - `GET /api/files?path=...` -- File listing\n  - `GET /api/files/*path` -- File download\n  - `GET /health` -- Health check (unauthenticated)\n- **Authentication**: All `/api` routes require JWT (RSA) via `Authorization: Bearer <token>` header\n- **Security**: Path sanitization prevents directory traversal outside workspace jail\n- **CLI flags**: `-port` (default 8080), `-workspace` (default CWD)\n- **Environment variable**: `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` -- PEM-encoded RSA public key (required at startup, fatal if missing)\n\n### Dockerfile for PicoD (from `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/deployment/design.md`):\n- Builder stage: `golang:1.24.4`, builds from `./cmd/picod`\n- Runtime stage: `ubuntu:24.04` with `python3` installed, **runs as root** (for chattr on pubkey + sandbox permissions)\n- Image name: `picod:latest`\n\n### Makefile targets:\n- `docker-build-picod`, `docker-buildx-picod`, `docker-push-picod`\n\n---\n\n## 3. Existing Proposals and Design Docs\n\n### Top-level proposals:\n| File | Path |\n|------|------|\n| AR-001 Proposal | `/home/dsj/benchmark/proposal.md` |\n| AR-001 through AR-015+ proposals | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-*/proposal.md` |\n\n### Design documents:\n| File | Path |\n|------|------|\n| Code Execution (PicoD) Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/code-execution/design.md` |\n| Sandbox Orchestration Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/sandbox-orchestration/design.md` |\n| Session Routing Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/session-routing/design.md` |\n| Session Store Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/session-store/design.md` |\n| Deployment Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/deployment/design.md` |\n| Idle Cleanup Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/idle-cleanup/design.md` |\n| CI/CD Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/ci-cd/design.md` |\n| CLI Toolkit Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/cli-toolkit/design.md` |\n| Integrations Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/integrations/design.md` |\n| Python SDK Design | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/python-sdk/design.md` |\n| AR-015 PicoD Command Execution API (stub) | `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/proposal.md` |\n\n### Specification documents:\n| File | Path |\n|------|------|\n| Code Execution (PicoD) Spec | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/code-execution/spec.md` |\n| Sandbox Orchestration Spec | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/sandbox-orchestration/spec.md` |\n| Session Routing Spec | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/session-routing/spec.md` |\n| Deployment Spec | `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/deployment/spec.md` |\n\n---\n\n## 4. CRD Types for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n\nAll types are in API group `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`, version `v1alpha1`.\n\n### AgentRuntime (`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agent_type.go`)\n\n```go\ntype AgentRuntime struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort     `json:\"targetPort,omitempty\"`\n    Template           *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\"`\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`      // default: \"15m\"\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`   // default: \"8h\"\n}\n\ntype SandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels      map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n    Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n    Spec        corev1.PodSpec    `json:\"spec\"`\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype AgentRuntimeList struct { ... Items []AgentRuntime ... }\n```\n\n### CodeInterpreter (`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go`)\n\n```go\ntype CodeInterpreter struct {\n    metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n    metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n    Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n    Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n    Ports              []TargetPort                    `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n    Template           *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n    SessionTimeout     *metav1.Duration                `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`      // default: \"15m\"\n    MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration                `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`   // default: \"8h\"\n    WarmPoolSize       *int32                          `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n    AuthMode           AuthModeType                    `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`             // enum: \"picod\" | \"none\"\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n    Labels           map[string]string             `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n    Annotations      map[string]string             `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n    RuntimeClassName *string                       `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n    Image            string                        `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n    ImagePullPolicy  corev1.PullPolicy             `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n    ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n    Environment      []corev1.EnvVar               `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n    Command          []string                      `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n    Args             []string                      `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n    Resources        corev1.ResourceRequirements   `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n}\n\ntype CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n    Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n    Ready      bool               `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n}\n```\n\n### Shared Types (`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/shared_types.go`)\n\n```go\ntype ProtocolType string\nconst (\n    ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n    ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n)\n\ntype AuthModeType string\nconst (\n    AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n    AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n)\n\ntype TargetPort struct {\n    PathPrefix string       `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n    Name       string       `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n    Port       uint32       `json:\"port\"`\n    Protocol   ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## 5. Existing Deployment and Command Execution Related Code\n\n### Deployment-related code:\n\n**WorkloadManager** (`pkg/workloadmanager/handler/`):\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/sandbox_create.go` -- Sandbox creation handler (693 lines), handles `POST /v1/agent-runtime` and `POST /v1/code-interpreter`\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/constants.go` -- GVR constants, kind constants, label/annotation constants\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/workloadmanager/handler/models.go` -- Request/response models\n\n**Router** (`pkg/router/`):\n- `/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/pkg/router/jwt.go` -- JWT manager (key generation, token signing/validation, K8s Secret persistence)\n- Session routing, reverse proxy, load balancing, middleware\n\n**Helm Chart**:\n- Templates described in `/home/dsj/benchmark/specs/deployment/design.md`\n- Three images: `workloadmanager`, `agentcube-router`, `picod`\n\n### Command execution related code:\n\n**PicoD auth injection in WorkloadManager** (`sandbox_create.go`, lines 273-278 and 567-618):\n```go\nif template.Spec.AuthMode == runtimev1alpha1.AuthModePicoD {\n    if err := h.injectPicodAuthEnv(sandboxCR, sandboxReq.Namespace, h.kubeClientset); err != nil {\n        // returns 401\n    }\n}\n```\nThe `injectPicodAuthEnv` function reads the Router's RSA public key from the K8s Secret `picod-router-identity` and injects it as the `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` environment variable into the sandbox pod's first container.\n\n**PicoD execution flow** (from spec):\n1. Router signs a JWT with `session_id` claim and forwards request to sandbox\n2. PicoD (inside sandbox) verifies the JWT using its `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY`\n3. PicoD executes the command via `exec.CommandContext` with timeout, captures stdout/stderr\n4. Returns `ExecuteResponse` with `stdout`, `stderr`, `exit_code`, `duration`, `start_time`, `end_time`\n\n---\n\n## 6. What \"PicoD\" Means in This Context\n\n**PicoD** (pronounced \"pico-dee\") is the **lightweight command execution daemon** that runs inside each sandbox pod in AgentCube. It is the innermost component of the architecture:\n\n```\nClient / SDK / CLI\n  -> Router (Deployment :8080)\n     <-> Redis/Valkey (session store)\n     -> WorkloadManager (Service :8080)\n        -> K8s API: CRDs, Sandbox, Pod, Secret, TokenReview\n  Sandbox Pod\n     -> PicoD (container :8080)  <-- HERE\n```\n\n### Key PicoD characteristics:\n- **Name origin**: \"Pico\" (smallest metric prefix) + \"D\" (Daemon) -- a minimal, focused daemon\n- **Role**: The code execution engine inside sandbox containers; receives JWT-authenticated HTTP requests and executes commands in a jailed workspace\n- **Authentication mode**: `AuthModePicoD` (\"picod\") is one of two auth modes for CodeInterpreter CRs (the other being `AuthModeNone`)\n- **Identity Secret**: The Router's RSA key pair is stored in K8s Secret named `picod-router-identity`\n- **Public key injection**: When `AuthMode == \"picod\"`, the WorkloadManager injects the Router's public key as `PICOD_AUTH_PUBLIC_KEY` env var into the sandbox pod\n- **Not yet implemented as Go code**: The `pkg/picod/` and `cmd/picod/` directories do not exist in the current workspace snapshot, but AR-015 (`/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_alibaba-cn-qwen3.6-plus_20260410T073331Z/changes/AR-015/`) is the stub proposal for \"PicoD Command Execution API\"\n- **Reference implementation exists**: The design docs reference `/tmp/agentcube-ref` as a reference clone containing the actual PicoD implementation\n</task_result>","metadata":{"sessionId":"ses_287ca0112ffebH4ZRvUNS1F2UU","model":{"modelID":"qwen3.6-plus","providerID":"alibaba-cn"},"truncated":false},"title":"Explore agentcube project structure","time":{"start":1775838297834,"end":1775838430859}}}}
